Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然如此还是一定有弱小的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那就保护他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这才能表现我们的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}强者出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最酷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}崭新的最强的NO.1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}的确从今天起 我就是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢ならあるはずだ　あなたにも僕にでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每个人都有梦想 你我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見つかりにくいだけだ忙しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但因为太忙而很难被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ミエナイチカラで　だれもが強く繋がっている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谁都被看不到的力量强力的连接着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何も大したことじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいても離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论是否在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昨日　今日　明日と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昨天 今天 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔のあなたはいつでも　この胸にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑容永远深印在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}You've got to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's never too late
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never say die